{"type":null,"faqId":45362,"title":"荣耀盒子M321连接音频设备后，没有声音?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>如果没有声音，可能是 AV 接口被设置为 CVBS 音视频输出模式，请进入“</span><span class=\"s1\">设置 &gt; 播放 &gt; AV 音视频</span><span>”，选择 “</span><span class=\"s1\">SPDIF 音频源码输出</span><span>”或 “</span><span class=\"s1\">SPDIF 音频解码输出</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164875\" style=\"width:4.026389in;height:2.2659721in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>“SPDIF 音频源码输出”声音直接由音频设备处理。如果您的音频设备很高级，能更好的处理声音，建议设置为该选项。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>“SPDIF 音频解码输出”声音由盒子处理。如果您的音频设备比较普通，没有盒子的能力强，建议设置为该选项。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":248,"faqType":"声音","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"883","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Sound","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556876000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":9,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"音频设备,声音,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}